Barclays May Abandon Battle Over Insurance, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-05-08T07:40:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-08/barclays-may-abandon-battle-over-insurance-telegraph-reports.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  may drop out of the legal
battle to defend its sales of personal protection insurance,
the  Daily Telegraph  said.  Barclays may say as early as tomorrow that it’s abandoning
the legal defense against allegations that thousands of clients
were wrongly sold insurance they didn’t need, the paper said,
citing unidentified industry officials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
